==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sciotheric
<hw>Sci`o*ther"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. L.
<ets>sciothericon</ets> a sundial. See <er>Sciatheric</er>.]</ety>
<def>Of or pertaining to a sundial.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Sciotheric telescope</b></col> <fld>(Dialing)</fld>,
<cd>an instrument consisting of a horizontal dial, with a telescope
attached to it, used for determining the time, whether of day or
night.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scious</ent>⟦br⟧
